---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于 lhy 的一些信息">
  <section class="pt-28 pb-8 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-block w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-5xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-glow animate-float">
        👨‍💻
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black gradient-text mb-4">关于我</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">一个热爱编程的普通人</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>👋</span>
          <span>你好！</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="prose-content">
          <p>我是 lhy，一名对技术充满热情的开发者。这个博客是我记录学习笔记、分享编程经验和生活感悟的地方。</p>
          <p>我相信知识应该被自由分享，也希望通过文字记录下自己成长的足迹，与志同道合的朋友们交流。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>🎯</span>
          <span>我的兴趣</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💻</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">编程开发</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📚</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">学习研究</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎮</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">游戏</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎵</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">音乐</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📖</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">阅读</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">✍️</div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">写作</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>🌐</span>
          <span>联系方式</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/linhongyu3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
            <div class="text-2xl">🐙</div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">GitHub</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">@linhongyu3</div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:linhongyu3@outlook.com" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
            <div class="text-2xl">📧</div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Email</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">linhongyu3@outlook.com</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>🛠️</span>
          <span>关于本站</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="prose-content">
          <p>本博客使用 <strong>Astro</strong> + <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> 构建，支持 GitHub Pages 静态部署。</p>
          <p>主要特点：</p>
          <ul>
            <li>✨ 现代化玻璃拟态设计</li>
            <li>🌙 深色/浅色主题切换</li>
            <li>⚡ 极致的加载速度</li>
            <li>📱 完美的移动端适配</li>
            <li>⬇️ 内置下载中心与镜像加速</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
